GuideContent.title: Introduction
GuideContent.description: Welcome to fat baby walkthrough, it will help you to know everything about fat baby simulator.you will find many tricks and walkthroughs. moreover, in this guide, you will discover how to complete all fat baby games levels in the easiest way.This guide is for everyone, not just for pros and beginners, but both alike. This guide will teach you everything you need to know about feed and grow, and how to be amazing at the game. If you are ready, then lets jump right in with the first section.

GuideContent.title: Note
GuideContent.description: This guide will be updated regularly along with the Feed and Grow: Fish updates. If a new update comes up, make sure to check out this guide to see what's new.

GuideContent.title: The basics
GuideContent.description: There are currently 3 modes you can play in Feed and Grow: Fish, and those are the survival mode, deathmatch mode, and crab madness. Survival is currently being worked on

GuideContent.title: About This Game
GuideContent.description: This game mode can be played on any map and is the mode you are probably going to be spending most of your time on until survival is released again. The basic concept is that you are a fish trying to survive in one of the four maps, and you have to find food and grow bigger in order to survive.

GuideContent.title: Saving builds & Clearing objects
GuideContent.description: You can save and paste builds. Saved builds can be pasted at any time, including in different game sessions, and as many times as you want.To save builds, click and hold down on the screen and drag to create a green box.
